''' Comfort Ekpo ''' (yin jiji to azan wiawetọ, Abọ̀húsun, Owhe 1954) Eyin ayinamẹtọ to Wehọmẹ Alavọ tọn Uyo tọn.

==Otàn gbẹzan etọn tọn==
Comfort Memfin Ekpo yin jiji to Uyo to 1954. Mẹjitọ etọn lẹ wẹ Etim Udoh Isok podo Nyong Sam Akpanpo. E bẹjẹeji taidi Sunday School teacher podọ e sọ sẹn taidi mẹplọntọ alọgọtọ tọn to wehọmẹ alavọ tọn Cross River tọn mẹ sọn 1983 jẹ 1991.
Ekpo wa lẹzun mẹbọdo azinponọgo ẹnẹtọ to wehọmẹ alavọ tọn Uyo tọn podọ yọnnusi tintan he yin mẹbọdo azinponọgo. To Awewesun owhe 2015 tọn mẹ, tito yin bibasi na ẹn nado yi dile Weyọnẹntọ Enefiok Essien ko yin didehẹlẹ taidi successor etọn.
Humọ, e kanwe hla Minister of Education, Adamu Adamu bo biọ dọdọ tito he yin bibasi na successor etọn lọ ni yin alọhẹndotena whẹ.
Ehe wẹ na whẹho  accusations of sexual assault and forgery allegedly he yin bibasi gado  Essien go he yin hodọdego gbọn linlindọtọ lẹ dali wutu.

